snippet.title: Inner Worlds gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Inner Worlds, Dos PC game produced by Sleepless Software in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/inner-worlds/6159/
Exploring and jumping around in this inventive platform adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
